## Enforcement

### Violations

If you become aware of a violation of this license:
1. Contact the copyright holder at ilan.dahn@gmail.com
2. Provide details of the suspected violation
3. Allow reasonable time for investigation and response

### Remedies

In case of violation, the copyright holder reserves the right to:
- Request immediate cessation of the violating activity
- Request removal of infringing materials
- Pursue legal remedies if necessary
- Publicly identify violators to protect the community

### Good Faith

This license is designed to keep The Methodology free and accessible. The copyright holder will interpret edge cases in favor of free use and knowledge sharing, not restriction.

